name: Roller skating
description:
Roller skating is one of the activities that is still practiced in the streets of Mexico City, since parks and roads have been built to be able to travel throughout the city exclusively for rollerbladers who like to go anywhere. side on skates, skateboard, bicycle, or any vehicle that has wheels, yes, hoverboards also fall into this category.

Without a doubt, skating is an experience that releases adrenaline, and it is a good exercise to do any day of the week, which requires agility, coordination, balance, dexterity and reflexes.
